Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:55.65,Default,,0,0,90,,On a spring night Virgo is spread out widely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:01.03,Default,,0,0,90,,My favorite star, Spica, is this Alpha star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,90,,If you stretch this line from the Big\NDipper, there's the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:10.83,Default,,0,0,90,,And if you pud the handle of the ladle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,90,,there's the star of the cow herder, Arcturus, then Spiea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:20.05,Default,,0,0,90,,This line is called the Great Arc of Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:25.51,Default,,0,0,90,,During the cherry blossom season\Ntry looking for it in the southern sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:31.98,Title,,0,0,90,,Marika and Marika
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,90,,Just as I thought, wrthout a compass, it's hard to figure out where I am or which direction I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,90,,This... I feel like I've seen a similar rock before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,90,,Could it be that I've been going around in circles?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.64,Default,,0,0,90,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,90,,No one's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.65,Default,,0,0,90,,I wonder how everyone is doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,90,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,90,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.75,Default,,0,0,90,,Okay, this will work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.54,Default,,0,0,90,,going down the same path I took before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.54,Default,,0,0,90,,With this. I'll know without a doubt if I m
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,90,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,90,,I'll get through this somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,90,,Oh man! Someone do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,90,,I keep going and going, but it's just more forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.35,Default,,0,0,90,,I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,90,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,90,,Damn it flow is this supposed to be training?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.66,Default,,0,0,90,,I'll definitely make them reimburse me for my glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,90,,the little seagull's doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,90,,Now that that's done.. I wonder how
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,90,,Is it all over for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,90,,I wanted to go to space...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.18,Default,,0,0,90,,I wanted to go to space..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,90,,I wanted to go to space~.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:15.48,Default,,0,0,90,,You can't go to space alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,90,,I thought I could go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,90,,I thought the only way to go was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,90,,I mean, I was... always alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.57,Default,,0,0,90,,Let's promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.66,Default,,0,0,90,,it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,90,,Pro...mise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,90,,Yep, Marika-chan, it's a promise to graduate school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,90,,And a promise to go to space together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,90,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.51,Default,,0,0,90,,I can... go together with people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,90,,I can... go as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.98,Default,,0,0,90,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,90,,Were friends with the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,90,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,90,,Surely we can definitely go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,90,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,90,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,90,,I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,90,,Doyour best, Marika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,90,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.66,Default,,0,0,90,,Do your best, for your dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.95,Default,,0,0,90,,I'm always here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,90,,I'm always with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,90,,So don't give up, Marika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,90,,What would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.72,Default,,0,0,90,,Quit meddling in my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,90,,I... I... have to apologize..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,90,,Apologize... then... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.86,Default,,0,0,90,,I have to tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.07,Default,,0,0,90,,that I want to go to space together, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,90,,That... looked like it was written a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,90,,Nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.02,Default,,0,0,90,,It's just as it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.53,Default,,0,0,90,,It's just that time has passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,90,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,90,,After some time, that girl stopped coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,90,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,90,,Her chronic disease took a turn for the worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,90,,.and she was to leave the country to get some treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,90,,I wanted to meet her again before that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,90,,That's what I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,90,,In the end that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,90,,That girl never came back to this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,90,,that she died overseas or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,90,,After a while, the adults were gossiping
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,90,,I knew of those rumors... but who knew\NIf that was even true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.85,Default,,0,0,90,,They're so alike, it looks as it she was reborn anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:54.61,Default,,0,0,90,,And the little one's friend also had\Nthe same name as her... Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,90,,Is it just by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,90,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,90,,It must be a coincidental resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,90,,First of all, even with the same name, this Marika\Nand that Marika's ages are too different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,90,,It's not like she's a ghost, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,90,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,90,,Did I break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,90,,Ukita... Marika...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,90,,Then... she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,90,,It can't be... such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,90,,I won't give in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,90,,Not at a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,90,,I don't want to give up.
Comment: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:33.98,Title,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,90,,I walked around all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,90,,but it definitely seems much larger than the map showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:55.89,Default,,0,0,90,,I'd be able to clearly tell where I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:55.89,Default,,0,0,90,,If I could at least find this river
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:13:00.77,Default,,0,0,90,,I don tthink the direction that the sun rose was wrong, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:07.03,Default,,0,0,90,,and move forward tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:07.03,Default,,0,0,90,,I'll just have to leave this tent behind
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,90,,Even if I have to go a long way I need to go\Nto a high place and confirm my location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey you're really there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.22,Default,,0,0,90,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,90,,The sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:31.32,Default,,0,0,90,,Thank goodness. Now I can begin to find out where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.33,Default,,0,0,90,,The first emergency landing site is around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,90,,The sea is on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,90,,A small hill in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:44.04,Default,,0,0,90,,That means I'm on this mountain-..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,90,,If that's the case, it seems like there\Nisn't much distance to the goal but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,90,,The time I have to make it there is limited...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:56.60,Default,,0,0,90,,.and with these mountain paths, it might take me all five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,90,,Speaking of which, I wonder if there's some\Nsign or flag to mark where location A is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,90,,It doesn't say anything here..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.54,Default,,0,0,90,,I wonder how everyone is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,90,,Now that I think about it, since I came to the Space\NSchool I never really had a meal by myscIf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,90,,I'm by myself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:39.43,Default,,0,0,90,,This is the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,90,,You ran too fast in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.15,Default,,0,0,90,,That's why you became exhausted halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,90,,Put I wanted to reach the goal quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,90,,That sort of feeling is also important...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,90,,but I always make sure to reach\Nthe goa|with half of my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,90,,Half of my strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,90,,To go to space, you need a lot of friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.67,Default,,0,0,90,,That swhy I leave halfof my strength for the rest of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,90,,So even if you reach the goal first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,90,,you can go back to lend them a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,90,,If you turn around to see your friend on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,90,,You can't go to space alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.65,Default,,0,0,90,,Half of my strength for my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.48,Default,,0,0,90,,For my friends who are somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,90,,The sound of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.84,Default,,0,0,90,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:43.39,Default,,0,0,90,,The river is flowing in this direction, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,90,,Thank goodness. It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.86,Default,,0,0,90,,If I go this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,90,,Someone was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.74,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey! Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.95,Default,,0,0,90,,Is anybody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,90,,That person must be like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,90,,Moving toward the goal marked as location A on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,90,,1 wasn't alone after all. I wasn't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,90,,Everyone's doing their best here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.56,Default,,0,0,90,,I have to go as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,90,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,90,,My feet won't hold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.96,Default,,0,0,90,,It must be because I haven't eaten anything since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:57.72,Default,,0,0,90,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,90,,Would I be able to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,90,,But if I get sick from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.65,Default,,0,0,90,,I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,90,,Not here anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,90,,Is anyone nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,90,,Isn't anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.96,Default,,0,0,90,,As I thought, they wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,90,,That person would have gone ahead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.22,Default,,0,0,90,,I wonder who was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:51.56,Default,,0,0,90,,I wonder if that person has already reached location A...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,90,,I'll have to do my best or I'll be left behind by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,90,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.79,Signs,,0,0,90,,Hashimoto General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,90,,W-Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.73,Default,,0,0,90,,Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,90,,Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.57,Default,,0,0,90,,I told you. Don't leave this room without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,90,,But, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.95,Default,,0,0,90,,I will not tolerate back-talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,90,,If it was the real Marika, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.09,Default,,0,0,90,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.42,Default,,0,0,90,,Why does he cay that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,90,,I'm myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.88,Default,,0,0,90,,i'm Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.06,Default,,0,0,90,,You're mistaken.
